{"tid":378424,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"與黎諾懿、余迪偉撞樣  陳曉東點答？","createTime":"2017-08-28T13:07:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-28T14:01:43.000Z","uid":14730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"077a67b9fb39e99623c1da40df5d49e136aac485","tid":378424,"uid":14730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T13:07:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/28/210549_4ea774b0e17c7168b4ec0e59c5bf4b3f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F28%2F210549_4ea774b0e17c7168b4ec0e59c5bf4b3f.png&h=6feaec85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n陳曉東在《天下第一Friend》中表示自己平日工作繁忙，亦懶得理會整容傳聞，更表示整容後需要時間消腫，加上自己入行20年，根本不必要搞這些。同時主持鄭紹康又追問他經常與藝人「撞臉」，例如初出道似梁詠琪，最近又被指似黎諾懿及電台DJ余迪偉，對此他直言：「是但啦！」<br />\n<br />\n陳曉東近年在內地有不錯的成績，不過東東也經歷過低潮，他說:「有部戲在上海的邊皮城市上映，三天便落畫了，回到家中，爸爸問我是否很需要錢用，這一句話我現在仍記得。他說：『你拍的戲連劉德華啲爛片都不如!』。」陳曉東明白父親是用激漲法，不過他明白世上沒有不好的角色，只有不好的演員。<br />\n<br />\n片：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2xGlYx4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2xGlYx4&d=3qOPseODpM7ZIU44cv8JVJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=3d48d073\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2xGlYx4</a>"},{"pid":"07d2b4f088ae690242b1abd8758145bd4a5c0636","tid":378424,"uid":92,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T13:17:37.000Z","msg":"你拍的戲連劉德華啲爛片都不如<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c35ce2d5338318fb53dc334eb6ecfce0630953fa","tid":378424,"uid":25754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T13:30:46.000Z","msg":"你拍的戲連劉德華啲爛片都不如<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63dc9f3b9a1805dd6ddc95911d559d9d0461f1af","tid":378424,"uid":63670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T13:34:32.000Z","msg":"再爛既片有華dee都<br />\n值得入場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"796b2d5dd5528a1c3dfe6f582a303837cd0c5e45","tid":378424,